  Siga Technologies Inc. (SIGA)  shouldn’t
have to hand over 50 percent of the profits from a smallpox
medicine to rival  PharmAthene Inc. (PIP) , lawyers for the drugmaker
told an appeals court today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
